      <h1 class="cn-title">Diet</h1>
      What we eat doesn’t just affect our physical health: it can also affect our mental health and wellbeing.
      Eating well – which means having a balanced diet full of vegetables and nutrients – can improve your sense of
      wellbeing and your mood.
   </section>
